OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,F"I'm angry, I'm sad that this is what
OL,7,Fmy life has to be... especially at my
OL,8,Fage," says Sophie Zenonos.
OL,10,F"There's so much that I want to do."
OL,12,FSophie was living a typical life of
OL,13,Fsomeone in their early 20s. She had
OL,14,Fjust married her husband, worked a
OL,15,Ffull-time job, in Essex, regularly
OL,16,Fworked out at the gym and was an avid
OL,17,Ffollower of her beloved football team,
OL,18,FTottenham Hotspur.
OL,20,FThen everything changed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
