OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781179881
OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,FShe told ITV Meridian: "No-one would
OL,7,Fsee that (cancer) because you would
OL,8,Flook at me and go 'physically you look
OL,9,Ffine, so you must be fine.'
OL,11,F"But there's a lot of ongoing trauma I
OL,12,Fguess as well as the physical
OL,13,Fsensations that you would get.
OL,15,F"My close family are the only people
OL,16,Fthat see the realities when I can't
OL,17,Fwalk up the stairs and my husband's
OL,18,Fcarrying me up there."
OL,26,@oD@JpmoD@Qpn
