OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781179881
OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,FIt comes as the charity Macmillan
OL,7,FCancer Support has warned of a hidden
OL,8,Fcancer crisis, with new data showing
OL,9,Fthat 51% of cancer patients in the
OL,10,FSouth of England are struggling with
OL,11,Fthe day-to-day impacts of living with
OL,12,Fthe disease.
OL,14,FConcerns expressed in the research
OL,15,Finclude poor sleep, managing finances,
OL,16,Fjuggling work, as well as issues
OL,17,Fsurrounding body confidence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
