PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781179881
OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,FThe organisation wants to introduce
OL,7,Fcancer training for 50,000 people in
OL,8,Fhigh street shops and pharmacies to
OL,9,Fhelp spark conversations around
OL,10,Fcancer, and connect people with
OL,11,Fsupport services.
OL,13,FProfessor Richard Simcock, Macmillan
OL,14,FChief Medical Officer, told ITV
OL,15,FMeridian the government, local
OL,16,Fbusinesses and communities will all be
OL,17,Fneeded to do what they can to help
OL,18,Faddress the issue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781179881
OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,FHe said: "Why now? Because this
OL,7,Fproblem isn't going to go away. In
OL,8,Ffact, it's going to get bigger.
OL,10,F"We predict a 54% increase in the
OL,11,Fnumber of people living with cancer
OL,12,Fover the next 20 years, so that might
OL,13,Fmean an extra million people facing
OL,14,Fthese problems in the years to come.
OL,16,F"It's a problem we have to sort out."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
