PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781179881
OL,3,CWoman shares difficulties of battling
OL,4,Ccancer twice in her 20s
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,F(DCHS) spokesperson said: "Our
OL,8,FNational Cancer Plan will make sure
OL,9,Fcare is built around patients, not
OL,10,Fjust hospitals.
OL,12,F"That's why we're planning in future
OL,13,Fto connect patients directly to
OL,14,Fcharities like Macmillan through the
OL,15,FNHS App from the moment of diagnosis,
OL,16,Fso vital support will be just a tap
OL,17,Faway."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
